LogScanner is a multithreaded java program that scans one or multiple log files for specific words, generates a report 
("output/LogScanner_Report.html") according to a custom filter, and sends an email with the report attached. To configure 
LogScanner, please edit the "LogScanner.properties" file.

The LogScanner.zip file is a compressed eclipse project.  To run LogScanner, first edit the 
"LogScanner.properties" file, then run the com.logscanner.LogScanner.java Class.

If you have any questions, please email YBINSF@YAHOO.COM
